24T06:03:25.000Z","msg":"幾錢"},{"pid":"9161ff2005838b599d572c4e9d921430fa175181","tid":52462,"uid":13700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:04:13.000Z","msg":"你仲玩到電話嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8872791fd56f7ae9728a9ed46db4c9eacdb135","tid":52462,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:04:15.000Z","msg":"幾多度？"},{"pid":"749d3686c53e0fb00146a8d65161ea11e79a1e14","tid":52462,"uid":62818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"我一年前都做佐，好正<br />\n萬幾蚊就唔駛煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 散光400幾度，唔戴眼鏡同盲無分別"},{"pid":"ced5a1051b5a6c1398130bd771bef367df45ea5a","tid":52462,"uid":18628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"邊間做"},{"pid":"54c555a4da678d54773a511bca01ef71103b9ba3","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩感覺 點解要做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三日前先驗完眼今日就做，<br />\n做之前等左大半個鐘，都有啲緊張<br />\n上到部機果陣其實個心情重未準備好<br />\n跟住佢就升我上支槍度，佢叫我望住綠光<br />\n點知5秒都唔知有冇就射完，比想像中快<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想考紀律部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e7442b5a9184b1ae67c0119f6eee78574b7f74","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚唔驚？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少少啦，但等緊果陣，比我做先果個人勁快做完，醫生又話佢做得好好，又話傷口埋就好好，心唸邊有咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6f556077e10120a334a838218e162f69da218a","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChristmas 優惠兩萬七"},{"pid":"575d2770483b75b20e62be67f9c3002c7e3b6966","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你仲玩到電話嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做完果下大約300度咁但勁濛好似有霧咁<br />\n宜家100度咁但都有霧"},{"pid":"70c0af14f167e615fa0314d1e53c72071d400335","tid":52462,"uid":10804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一年前都做佐，好正<br />\n萬幾蚊就唔駛煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 散光400幾度，唔戴眼鏡同盲無分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n散光有冇話貴d<br />\n我都係散光勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0573027a9af1f25643db20b88015164202c5cce","tid":52462,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7508556be43840aa2782c7c4badcf40b548ab694","tid":52462,"uid":58918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你仲玩到電話嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做完果下大約300度咁但勁濛好似有霧咁<br />\n宜家100度咁但都有霧</blockquote><br />\n要幾耐先可以完全好哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0395fcf0b704129555ae8bea9030c2c6cab42367","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一年前都做佐，好正<br />\n萬幾蚊就唔駛煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 散光400幾度，唔戴眼鏡同盲無分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好期待霧氣快啲清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打smile 定lasik?"},{"pid":"a13d9d7748ddccb5e3efbe85cc9bf3bf85beb749","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香激"},{"pid":"d2bfc24e2b5efcdb720905211ad022b1b2954045","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:15:28.000Z","