 />\n<br />\n會唔會無得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbf39e261781b7d1d3e800a1a2c59f046698497","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你仲玩到電話嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做完果下大約300度咁但勁濛好似有霧咁<br />\n宜家100度咁但都有霧</blockquote><br />\n要幾耐先可以完全好哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話一星期會埋口，所以呢7日我對眼都唔濕得水，游水就一個月"},{"pid":"8302106022320aad1bbf6042a810ae129c4f9428","tid":52462,"uid":67069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"係咪跟深淺度收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我又近視(四五百左右又散光(兩百幾)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292766705b791832675a7af1621821027b57cd92","tid":52462,"uid":18856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"邊到做?"},{"pid":"530bdabf0ed92bf6072b750beafe80673a46daac","tid":52462,"uid":62818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我一年前都做佐，好正<br />\n萬幾蚊就唔駛煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 散光400幾度，唔戴眼鏡同盲無分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n散光有冇話貴d<br />\n我都係散光勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無，一樣價, 佢係散光同近視一次過做嗮<br />\n我係因為識人先平d<br />\n原價都要兩萬(兩隻眼做嗮)"},{"pid":"7f5c04c12f6766daf2d67615e89ec716da0dbd11","tid":52462,"uid":62818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇做完一兩年既巴打係到?<br />\n想問你宜家既度數有冇反彈?&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n近排有覆診，無反彈"},{"pid":"a3642f5935844dbef0cb427ec1d64ede910ab045","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n左眼700 近視 400散光<br />\n右眼就600 加300<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會唔會無得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要驗眼先知，角膜厚度好重要，如果天生比正常薄就算100度都唔做得，不過唔常見<br />\nSmile好似係近視散光加埋Max 1200<br />\nLASIK 再高啲好似1800<br />\n都係果句聽左講座驗眼先最實際"},{"pid":"975de9578649ab3e15dd8640876b4857ff91693a","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪跟深淺度收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我又近視(四五百左右又散光(兩百幾)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n劃一收費"},{"pid":"5748d1c3c52abed0d1c12d19f0860de774870f79","tid":52462,"uid":568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"點解要做激光<br />\n唔做可逆轉果隻？"},{"pid":"59b342943d5212d0e51c14b857ec710bae6f0f65","tid":52462,"uid":62818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n左眼700 近視 400散光<br />\n右眼就600 加300<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會唔會無得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做到<br />\n我問過醫生，過千度都可以做<br />\n白內障都可以"},{"pid":"515c9ac243aacb5f49b61f95d71d16d7dc6a3cad","tid":52462,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊到做?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面講左<br />\n香港激光矯視中心"},{"pid":"f0fe44c8be02f2b04d73b52dbf164306c9b151dc","tid":52462,"uid":62818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:27:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so